4.	Describe what an algorithm is and explain why it is a useful “tool” to translate from a human level problem (we can think of) to a computer program.
Algorithm is a procedure or formula for solving a problem. It’s useful for calculating a function calculations or other problem-solving operations, especially by a computer.


